commit.message: fsbuild/__init__.py, import non-std packages on demand
Remove macOS10.9 build target for FS-UAE Launcher 4.x, at least for now
Removed cacert.pem (should be handled by certifi package now)
Fix loading WHDLoad .lha archives on Windows
Controller config supports writing legacy configs
Added lots of static typing, some refactoring
Depend on specific versions of pip and pipenv
Hotplug controllers, updated config tool, use sdl mapping format
Updated missing pip3 modules for macOS (#117)
